{"tid":324953,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【炒市不炒股】面世4個月 槓桿及反向ETF已佔席位","createTime":"2017-07-17T00:21:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-17T00:28:17.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e0ae43033c3d366715ca003c844e22c5ef2fb315","tid":324953,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T00:21:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170716/large/1500212332_4d3a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170716%2Flarge%2F1500212332_4d3a.jpg&h=0a18130f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n除兩大港股ETF（指數買賣基金）及三大A股ETF外，其他港上市的ETF普遍成交均低迷，惟港股及A股的槓桿及反向（L&amp;I）產品自今年三月中面世至今4個月，已極速搶佔活躍成交ETF榜的前列位置，綜合16隻相關產品今年合共的日均成交額高達6.7億元，佔大市成交近0.9%。<br />\n<br />\nL&amp;I產品的表現，為追蹤指數的雙倍或反向回報，目前最活躍的L&amp;I產品為FL南方恒指（7200），日均成交額近1億元，其次FL南方國指（7288）及FL未來恒指（7231）日均亦有約八千萬元成交，惟三產品規模僅約2.4億元至3.5億元。而按彭博數據，同樣有槓桿的窩論及牛熊證今年日均交投佔大市比例約19%，去年則有24%。<br />\n<br />\n南方東英ETF及指數策略部首席策略師李梓維表示，南方東英已搶佔L&amp;I約五成市佔率，包括有對沖跌市風險的長倉基金，亦是反向產品的投資者，而隨着主題式ETF及L&amp;I面世，他指港ETF發展已進入第二階段，投資者不再只揀追蹤主要股指的ETF。但李梓維強調，L&amp;I與輪證非直接競爭對手，後者槓桿較高，前者則可填補市場上缺乏低槓桿投資產品的空白。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56964057&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170716\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56964057%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170716&d=pGABYCmRHTumhql11H3vyywN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=66d3044c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56964057%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170716&h=e959cbeb\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56964057&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170716</a>"},{"pid":"867018fffa0dc5bf97b37c5deb75ae8adb3acfb7","tid":324953,"uid":76855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T00:28:17.000Z","msg":"又打飛機"}]}